                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/9538.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Ambassador to France</gloss>
                        to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-11-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 4, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Ex-President Porfirio Díaz denies interview stating he would return to Mexico to
                    fight invasion. He has advised Huerta to subordinate self to country.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herrick</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
